Package: YouAnalyser
Title: Provide Standardized Analytics Products for YouGov DACH
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: 
    person(
        "Emmanuel", "Guizar Rosales",
        email = "emmanuel.guizar@yougov.ch",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(Position = "Data & Analytics Innovation Scientist")
    )
Description: A collection of functions that serve as tools for
    YouGov DACH Analytics Partners. The function currently provides functions
    for Key Driver Analysis. Planned addtions include
    Structural Equation Modeling, Implicit Association Tests,
    Segmentation (Cluster Analysis), and MaxDiff.
